007675PD.title: Intersection of William and Wellington Streets, Perth from the Horseshoe Bridge
007675PD.text: A sign advertises R.A. Jones (in the Post Office Directory Mrs R.A. Jones) as proprietor of the Royal Hotel opposite the Universal Shoe Stores. By the 1926 W.A. Post Office Directory the licensee of the Royal Hotel is M.E. Coombes.
